ISLAMABAD, May 31 (APP):Federal Minister for Information, Broadcasting, National Heritage and Culture Attaullah Tarar on Friday said Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif had chaired a meeting at 7:00 am regarding his visit to China.
In a post on social media network X, he said that during the meeting, he reviewed the preparations being made by ministries and Divisions regarding this important visit.
